      <title>Snap 股价因销售疲软和利润前景不佳而下跌</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2024-08-02/snap-shares-tumble-on-weaker-sales-profit-outlook-video</link>
      <description><![CDATA[Snap 股价在盘后交易中暴跌，此前该公司公布了令人失望的第二季度销售额，并给出了低于预期的当期收益前景。Insider Intelligence 的 Jasmine Enberg 与 Ed Ludlow 一起参加了“彭博科技”节目。（来源：彭博社）]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2024-08-02/snap-shares-tumble-on-weaker-sales-profit-outlook-video</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 02 Aug 2024 20:17:47 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>对冲基金在抛售中削减了 2022 年以来对布伦特原油看涨押注</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-02/hedge-funds-cut-bullish-brent-bets-most-since-2022-amid-selloff</link>
      <description><![CDATA[在算法抛售和对需求的担忧加剧的背景下，对冲基金对布伦特原油的看涨押注大幅减少，降幅为近两年来最大。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-02/hedge-funds-cut-bullish-brent-bets-most-since-2022-amid-selloff</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 02 Aug 2024 20:14:21 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>DoorDash 公布的利润前景强于预期</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2024-08-02/doordash-posts-stronger-than-expected-profit-outlook-video</link>
      <description><![CDATA[DoorDash 公布了本季度利润预测强于预期，证实客户需求强劲，进军餐厅以外的新领域的计划已取得成效，此后该公司股价创下 9 个月来最大单日涨幅。DoorDash 首席财务官 Ravi Inukonda 与 Ed Ludlow 一起参加“彭博科技”节目。（来源：彭博社）]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2024-08-02/doordash-posts-stronger-than-expected-profit-outlook-video</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 02 Aug 2024 20:12:20 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>Booking 首席执行官讨论前景和收益</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2024-08-02/booking-ceo-discusses-outlook-earnings</link>
      <description><![CDATA[Booking Holdings Inc. 是 Kayak 和 Priceline 等近十几个旅游品牌的母公司，尽管其第二季度业绩大多超出分析师预期，但第三季度的业绩预测却令人失望。该公司股价在周五交易中暴跌。首席执行官 Glenn Fogel 向彭博社表示。（来源：彭博社）]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2024-08-02/booking-ceo-discusses-outlook-earnings</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 02 Aug 2024 20:03:09 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>古根海姆：美国就业报告让美联储“更接近采取行动”</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2024-08-02/us-jobs-report-brings-fed-closer-to-action-guggenheim</link>
      <description><![CDATA[由于美国就业报告疲软，人们担心美联储维持利率在 20 年高位的决定可能会导致经济进一步放缓，股市抛售加剧，债券收益率下跌。摩根大通的 Kay Herr 和古根海姆合伙人的 Steve Brown 讨论了近期降息的可能性。他们与 Sonali Basak 就“彭博实际收益率”进行了交谈。（来源：彭博）]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2024-08-02/us-jobs-report-brings-fed-closer-to-action-guggenheim</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 02 Aug 2024 20:01:19 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>派拉蒙在 Skydance 收购文件争夺战中占据优势</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-02/paramount-global-gains-edge-in-fight-over-skydance-buyout-files</link>
      <description><![CDATA[派拉蒙全球公司 (Paramount Global) 准备拒绝向养老基金移交内部文件的要求，该要求引发了人们对该公司被天舞传媒 (Skydance Media) 以 24 亿美元收购的质疑，此次收购将这家著名好莱坞影业公司的控制权转移给制片人大卫·埃里森 (David Ellison)。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-02/paramount-global-gains-edge-in-fight-over-skydance-buyout-files</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 02 Aug 2024 19:32:56 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>纳斯达克 100 指数进入调整区间，人工智能宠儿股价下跌</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-02/nasdaq-100-is-in-correction-territory-with-ai-darlings-sinking</link>
      <description><![CDATA[大型科技公司的剧烈轮动导致纳斯达克 100 指数陷入回调区域，短短三周内市值蒸发逾 2 万亿美元，交易员平仓了一年多来获利颇丰的头寸。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-02/nasdaq-100-is-in-correction-territory-with-ai-darlings-sinking</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 02 Aug 2024 13:47:52 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>摩根士丹利因分析师梅奥下调评级而获得唯一看跌评级</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-02/morgan-stanley-gets-lone-bearish-call-as-wells-fargo-s-mayo-cuts</link>
      <description><![CDATA[摩根士丹利今年首次收到分析师的看跌评级，富国银行的迈克·梅奥将该股评级从“持股观望”下调至“减持”，并表示考虑到部分业务面临的压力，该股的估值看起来很高。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-02/morgan-stanley-gets-lone-bearish-call-as-wells-fargo-s-mayo-cuts</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 02 Aug 2024 13:13:10 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>就业疲软导致股市抛售加剧，债券上涨：市场总结</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-01/stock-market-today-dow-s-p-live-updates</link>
      <description><![CDATA[疲软的就业报告引发人们担忧，美联储维持利率在二十年高位的决定可能会导致经济进一步放缓，从而加剧了股市抛售，债券收益率下跌。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-01/stock-market-today-dow-s-p-live-updates</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 01 Aug 2024 22:41:21 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>MercadoLibre 股价上涨，成为拉丁美洲最有价值的公司</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-01/mercadolibre-meli-tops-estimates-with-profit-doubling-from-year-ago</link>
      <description><![CDATA[拉丁美洲大型电子商务和支付公司 MercadoLibre Inc. 的第二季度收益超出分析师预期，其股价飙升，超越巴西能源生产商巴西石油公司，成为该地区最有价值的公司。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-01/mercadolibre-meli-tops-estimates-with-profit-doubling-from-year-ago</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 01 Aug 2024 20:08:19 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
